descriptionNullable:
### Cosmos Image Dataset
This dataset is a simple collection of 3,600 space images for space image generation GANs.

Therefore, there is no additional labeling.

If you want to use this dataset for space image classification, you may need additional labeling.

If you need additional labeling, please contact ```boseoggim08@gmail.com``` and I can help you.

This dataset also includes unrealistic pictures. This is to make something beautiful even if it is unrealistic when creating an image with GAN.

Good luck!😆 

[Reference code](https://github.com/BOSOEK/Cosmos)
P.S. We will reinforce the data as soon as possible.
